UPSTREAM RELEASE

Make the changes the software
Edit IDMETA to set new version number X.Y or X.Y.Z
Edit upstream changelog (often "Changes" or "NEWS")
Edit any language-specific version designation
$ git tag vX.Y
$ git push origin tag vX.Y


DEBIAN RELEASE

$ ssh squeeze
$ cd proj/ZOOM-Perl
$ git pull
$ ~/proj/git-tools/id-deb-build/mkdist.sh
$ sudo rm -rf deb-src
$ ~/proj/git-tools/id-deb-build/id-mk-deb-src.sh
$ time sudo ~/proj/git-tools/id-deb-build/id-pbuild.sh
	# NO NOT specify build platforms: IDMETA has this
$ ~/proj/git-tools/id-deb-build/id-pbuild.sh --upload


